{"title":"悼芦芒同志","authors":["臧克家"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":3,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"悼芦芒同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧克家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"京华同堂座谈诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算一算才有几多日子？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手握手，面对面："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“您年龄变了，样子没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有变”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说：“您是三十年代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我呢，属于五十年间”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你精力旺，体躯健，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限才华待开展。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“攀登犹自脚力健，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只计前程不计年！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我念了自己的两个诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你侧耳倾听，笑满脸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知道我酷爱老牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你送我一纸水牛画卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我珍惜你的手迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不时地展开观看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你回上海不久，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听说要去海南岛参观，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我等着你的新作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等来的却是讣告短函！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“出师未捷身先死”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为千古遗恨的名言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你画上的水牛呜呜地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪水模糊了我的双眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九七九年二月二十六日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}